law.history: Repealed 1950 Ky. Acts ch. 68, sec. 12, effective March 15, 1950. -- Created 1948 Ky. Acts ch. 110, sec. 3, effective July 1,1948.

metadata.catchline-at-repeal: Coin machine licenses required; who to procure; seals; instructions as to use of machine and what user will receive; illegal machines not permitted; exemption of machines in warehouses.
